These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, video-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, bartender
1. the nurse is in an even position##4
2. the bartender is the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | video-games | camping |
| Job     | bartender    | nurse   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, basketball
1. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | sprite | cola        |
| Sport      | golf  | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, r&b
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani
1. the japanese is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | country |
| Nationality   | japanese | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, cucumber
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | juice      | soy-milk |
| Food       | raspberry | cucumber    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, project-manager
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, japanese
1. the colombian is in an even position##4
2. the project-manager is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Job           | teacher | project-manager |
| Nationality   | japanese    | colombian         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, tennis
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, car
1. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | tennis | rowing  |
| Transport   | car  | tram |

 #################################

 
