.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, dutch
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, parkour
1. the dutch is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the egyptian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | dutch | egyptian   |
| Sport         | rugby | parkour |

